# bevanCircle

- _bevanCircle(g)_

Answer the Bevan circle of the reference triangle _t_.

Draw at right triangle:

~~~spl svg=A
let t = sssTriangle(3, 4, 5);
[
	t,
	t.bevanCircle,
	t.excircles
].LineDrawing
~~~

